prompt: Make a website for a institute that primarily focuces on coding, development and DSA.
refinedPrompt: Create a website for an institute that specializes in teaching coding, software development, and data structures and algorithms (DSA). The website should have a modern design, be responsive, and include the following pages: Home, About Us, Courses, Faculty, Resources, and Contact Us. The Home page should provide an overview of the institute, highlight key offerings, and include a call-to-action for prospective students. The Courses page should list available programs, including course descriptions, durations, and prerequisites. The website should also feature student testimonials, a blog with coding tips and industry insights, and a contact form for inquiries.
